Class Predator

java.lang.Object
Animal
Predator
Direct Known Subclasses:
LandPredator, Shark
public class Predator extends Animal
The Predator class represents a specific type of animal that is a predator. It extends the Animal class and includes additional information about the number of penguins the predator has killed.
